<div class="pad clear">
<h3>Parking</h3>
<p>There are large car parks for patients and visitors, for which charges apply. To view charges, please vlew our website. Some visitors are exempt from payment: eg: parents staying overnight with very sick children; patients undergoing treatment such as radiotherapy; parents feeding babies on the Neo Natal Unit. <br/>The Trust has 256 parking spaces for the public and 58 spaces for disabled          http://www.gloshospitals.nhs.uk/content/transport.html</p>
